title: IPL Complete Patch For EA Cricket 2008 by Laststayer & mjknightr
description:
EA Sports Cricket 2008 Indian Premier League Patch
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Contents in this patch:-

1. This patch has got all the IPL teams with their correct logos, and 7 predicted kits .

2.Most of the international players have their original faces.

3.New International Logos ( never seen before)

4.New overlays & new shots in the game.

5.International teams squads are up to date & their abilities also changed.

6.All new players like Ishan sharmna, Misbah- ul- haq , Virat kohli.(all IPL contracted players in it.)

7.New IPL menu with cricket 08 look.

And Many More Which Can't Be Written.




Enjoyyyyy....
